<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="User Registration Email Template." />
  <title>INAE Reference Request</title>
  <style type="text/css">
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f2f3f8;
      font-family: "Open Sans", sans-serif;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      width: 100% !important;
      height: 100% !important;
    }

    table {
      border-spacing: 0;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    img {
      display: block;
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline !important;
    }

    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 570px;
      width: 100%;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      padding: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      background-color: #e9ecef;
    }

    .logo {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .divider {
      border-top: 1px solid #cecece;
      margin: 25px 0;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .button {
      background: #402e7a;
      text-decoration: none !important;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 14px;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 20px auto 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .footer p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgba(69, 80, 86, 0.74);
      line-height: 18px;
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .email-wrapper {
        padding: 15px;
      }

      .button {
        font-size: 13px;
        padding: 10px 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div>
    <table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" class="email-wrapper">
      <tr>
        <td style="text-align: center; padding: 20px; background-color: #edf2fb">
          <a href="https://www.inae.in/" title="logo" target="_blank">
            <img width="400" src="https://www.inae.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logon.png" alt=""
              title="logo" />
          </a>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="background-color: #f5f3f4;">
        <td>
          <div style="padding: 18px;">
            <h4 style="font-size: 18px; color: #1e1e2d; font-weight: 700; text-align: left;">
              Dear <%= refereeFullName %>,
            </h4>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #1e1e2d; text-align: left; text-align: justify;">
              Greetings from Indian National Academy of Engineering (INAE)!
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #1e1e2d; text-align: justify;">
              We are reaching out to request your recommendation for <%= applicantName %> (<%= designation%>,<%= instituteName%>) who has applied for
                Individual Membership of INAE and has provided your contact details for reference purposes.
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #1e1e2d; text-align: justify;">
              The form can be accessed via the link below:
            </p>
            <p style="text-align: center;">
              <a href="<%= referenceFormUrl %>" class="button">Reference Form</a>
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #1e1e2d; text-align: justify;">
              You are requested to complete and submit the reference form at your earliest, but not
              later than a week as it has to be put forth the selection committee and subsequently
              get approved by the INAE Governing Council.
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #1e1e2d; text-align: justify;">
              Thank you for your assistance.
            </p>
            <div class="divider"></div>
            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #1e1e2d; text-align: left;">
              
              With regards,<br /><br />
              Secretariat<br />
              <strong>Indian National Academy of Engineering (INAE)</strong><br />
              Ground Floor, Block-II,<br />
              Technology Bhavan,<br />
              New Mehrauli Road,<br />
              New Delhi-110 016.<br />
              Phone: 011-26582475<br />
              Website: <a href="https://www.inae.in/"
                style="color: #402e7a; text-decoration: none;">www.inae.in</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="footer">
          <p>&copy; <a href="https://www.inae.in/"
              style="color: rgba(69, 80, 86, 0.74); text-decoration: none;"><strong>www.inae.in</strong></a></p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>
</body>

</html>